data.description: Take a step into your new Craftsman style home and you'll find yourself surrounded by comfort, convenience, and plenty of storage. This 3 year old roof is in great condition, ready for years of worry-free living. And when the summer heat sets in, you can relax knowing that this oasis comes complete with air conditioning! With an open floor plan, you'll have flexibility to make the space whatever suits your needs. Plus, with a finished basement (lots of extra storage!), shopping nearby on I5 and all the local amenities – there's nothing missing here! Come take a look at what could be yours today!
